@startuml US_4.1.7_SSD
autonumber

actor "Logistics\nOperator" as Operator
participant ":System" as System

== Select VVN ==
activate Operator
Operator -> System: Acede à secção "Approved VVNs"
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta lista de VVNs aprovadas
deactivate System
Operator -> System: Seleciona VVN da lista
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta detalhes da VVN
deactivate System

== Create VVE ==
Operator -> System: Clica em "Start Execution" e introduz hora real de chegada
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta confirmação de criação de VVE
deactivate System

== View VVE ==
Operator -> System: Acede à execução criada
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta detalhes da VVE (status, timings, operations)
deactivate System
deactivate Operator

@enduml
